Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever sort of hell my heart is living right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as usual, in the world around me, it's just another day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends laughing, feigning ignorance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in a dream with the name of solitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:01:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, waving my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit by bit, things started to fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of nothing but small failures,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd thought to myself that it'd be best to give up on it all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have the courage to quit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the feeling somewhere that I just shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet when looking at all these happy sceneries,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't cry; I can't cry - I'm sulking a little
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is truly alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We just attempt to isolate ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Slipping underneath the sheets of a cold bed, hiding away in our dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"How about you? Haven't given up yet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:03:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're not looking for promising excuses, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream I saw when I shut my eyes was one where I was all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you give up too much, you end up an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I won't give up on a single thing anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Solitude gives despair a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonlight - Paint in the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak - Even if the darkness obstructs the daybreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Choosing to smile all the time, I hesitated, unsure if I should show my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In attempting to become someone strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I sealed away my weak self and ended up all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be reborn in the daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your honest self is platinum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we awaken from this bad dream, splash water on yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and wash away that glum sleepy face
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever sort of hell my heart is living right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the world around me is giving me a trial to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Choosing to smile all the time, I hesitated, unsure if I should show my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In attempting to become someone strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I sealed away my weak self and ended up all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be reborn in the daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your honest self is platinum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we awaken from this bad dream, splash water on yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and wash away that glum sleepy face
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,dawns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak...
